ve |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106162937/http://ew.com/awards/2017/01/05/producers-guild-award-nominations-2017/ |archive-date=January 6, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/ca/news/903983/2018-producers-guild-award-nominations-the-full-list-of-film-and-tv-nominees |title=2018 Producers Guild Award Nominations: The Full List of Film and TV Nominees |last=Dupre |first=Elyse |date=5 January 2018 |website=E! News |access-date=5 January 2018}}</ref><br>Nominated\u2014[[British Academy Television Award for Best International Programme|BAFTA for Best International Programme]] (2013)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/2013/television |title=Television in 2013 |date=2013 |website=[[British Academy of Film and Television Arts]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401215822/http://awards.bafta.org/award/2013/television |archive-date=April 1, 2015 |access-date=April 12, 2017}}</ref><br>Nominated\u2014[[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Dramatic Series|Writers Guild of America Award for Dramatic Series]] (2011-2012, 2014\u20132016, 2018)<ref name=\"2011wga\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/wga-writers-guild-awards-winners-list-292639 |title=Writers Guild Awards: Complete Winners List |last=A. Fernandez |first=Jay |date=February 19, 2012 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120430092051/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/wga-writers-guild-awards-winners-list-292639 |archive-date=April 30, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/wga-announces-tv-nominations-398792 |title=WGA Announces TV Nominations |date=December 6, 2012 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121209043357/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/wga-announces-tv-nominations-398792 |archive-date=December 