 prize at Producers Guild of America awards |date=January 24, 2016 |work=[[Fox News]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406012822/http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2016/01/24/big-short-takes-home-top-prize-at-producers-guild-america-awards/ |archive-date=April 6, 2016}}</ref><br>[[Monte-Carlo Television Festival|Golden Nymph Awards]] for Outstanding International Producer (2012)<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/game-of-thrones-monte-carlo-tv-festival-winners-337899 |title=HBO's 'Game of Thrones,' 'Game Change' Win Top Prizes at Monte Carlo TV Festival |last=Leffler |first=Rebecca |date=June 14, 2012 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618172642/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/game-of-thrones-monte-carlo-tv-festival-winners-337899 |archive-date=June 18, 2012}}</ref><br>Nominated\u2014Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Drama Series (2011-2014)<ref name=\"emmys.com\" /><br>Nominated\u2014Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Drama Series (2011-2014)<ref name=\"emmys.com\" /><br>Nominated\u2014Producers Guild of America Award for Best Episodic Drama (2011-2014, 2016, 2018)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.producersguild.org/news/80252/PGA-ANNOUNCES-THEATRICAL-MOTION-PICTURE-AND-LONG-FORM-TELEVISION-NOMINATIONS-FOR-2012-PGA-AWARDS.htm |title=PGA Announced Theatrical Motion Picture and Long-Form Television Nominations for 2012 PGA Awards |date=January 3, 2012 |website=[[TVLine]] |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530154740/http://www.producersguild.org/news/80252/PGA-ANNOUNCES-THEATRICAL-MOTION-PICTURE-AND-LONG-FORM-TELEVISION-NOMINATIONS-FOR-2012-PGA-AWARDS.htm |archive-date=May 30, 2012 |access-date=April 12, 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://collider.com/2013-pga-nominations-homeland-modern-family/214302/ |title=Homeland, Game of Thrones, Modern Family, and Louie Lead Television Nominations for 2013 Producers Guild Awards |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |date=November 28, 2012 |website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130122041338/http://collider.com/2013-pga-nominations-homeland-modern-family/214302/ |archive-date=January 22, 2013 |access-date=April 12, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/tv-nominees-for-pga-awards-unveiled/ |title=TV Nominees For PGA Awards Unveiled |date=December 3, 2013 |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20131203193808/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/tv-nominees-for-pga-awards-unveiled/ |archive-date=December 3, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/american-sniper-birdman-boyhood-pga-awards-nominees-full-list-1201341195/ |title='American Sniper,' 'Birdman' & 'Boyhood' Among PGA Awards Nominees |date=January 5, 2015 |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108043959/http://deadline.com/2015/01/american-sniper-birdman-boyhood-pga-awards-nominees-full-list-1201341195/ |archive-date=January 8, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://ew.com/awards/2017/01/05/producers-guild-award-nominations-2017/ |title=People v. O.J., Stranger Things score Producers Guild Award nominations |last=DeSantis |first=Rachel |date=January 5, 2017 |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |access-date=April 12, 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106162937/http://ew.com/awards/2017/01/05/producers-guild-award-nominations-2017/ |archive-date=January 6, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/ca/news/903983/2018-producers-guild-award-nominations-the-full-list-of-film-and-tv-nominees |title=2018 Producers Guild Award Nominations: The Full List of Film and TV Nominees |last=Dupre |first=Elyse |date=5 January 2018 |website=